  "description": "Sledge's Shotgun is a legendary Bandit shotgun from the Borderlands 2 base game. It pairs Bandit's large magazine with a Dahl-style two-shot burst. Used at close range where all pellets land, its burst pattern, extra pellets, and high damage allow heavy spike damage. It is not fully automatic. After each burst there is a forced pause, and you must pull the trigger again to continue firing, so the listed fire rate can be misleading. This makes it less suitable for Gunzerkers relying on Keep Firing.",
