  "notes": "Each trigger pull fires a two-shot burst, and each shot consumes 2 ammo, so every burst uses 4 rounds. Fire rate bonuses also shorten the delay between bursts; even modest boosts (around +20 percent) are noticeable, including from fire rate accessories. It uses a Jakobs double barrel rather than a Bandit barrel. It can roll different accessories, but the prefix is not shown in the name. A 14/10/2013 hotfix increased Bandit shotgun magazine size by 1 and slightly improved reload speed.",
